# PlatinumRx Assignment

## Overview
This project demonstrates SQL, Excel, and Python skills.

## SQL
- Hotel & Clinic schema queries
- Used joins, aggregations, window functions

## Excel
- VLOOKUP for data mapping
- Time-based analysis using formulas

## Python
- Time conversion logic
- String duplicate removal

## Tools Used
- MySQL / PostgreSQL
- Excel / Google Sheets
- Python 3
